{"tid":2337372,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"惟有飲者L其M 同佢班弱智fans入一入黎。","createTime":"2020-12-23T08:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T06:48:27.000Z","uid":343520,"like":22,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"07a5f892194c2d75b4610f9fee0a6d854efe076d","tid":2337372,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T08:45:01.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">LM狗行為狗公，發情隨便騷擾女性</span></strong></span>，咁樣都扮睇唔到？請問你地做人係咪冇良知？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果咁都冇人指出，遲下係咪個個有錢有小小名氣就可以唔尊重女性？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>覺得我講錯嘅，自己睇</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/knVwRUc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FknVwRUc.png&h=c0cc9364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>請問下LM狗，你可以解釋下咩叫重酬未呢？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n你係街見到靚女食飯就鳩痕，周圍開po、開ig尋人我都算喇，最多當你係痴線佬，但你依家係講到明重酬喎，<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"x-large\">用利益誘使人做出不道德行為喎。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n依家人地食個飯咋喎，同你又咩關係都冇，你重酬尋人算係咩意思？江湖追殺令呀？<br />\n<br />\n如果有人為左錢而真係去用任何方法搵個女仔出黎，為左錢而去騷擾呢位女士，有冇諗過會對人地造成影響呀？<br />\n<br />\n人地食個飯就要比你件狗公騷擾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>麻煩LM狗呢次唔好再扮睇唔到，做返個男人啦，你一係出黎解釋，一係同人道歉。</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"f4d089d0ba80138a1f40d0114533e6219f6db428","tid":2337372,"uid":367153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T08:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa8e626f8f0a887dcab6de65e5ada40dfa24611","tid":2337372,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T08:50:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i